stemSummary"><span>Impacte<span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D=
"fbd2df0c-e2fb-41fd-817c-39119cab7599">d System</span> Summary</span></h2>
<p><span></span></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<div class=3D"plugin-tabmeta-details">
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 934=
.0px;">
