<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Cash Platform (<span><span class=3D"ui-provider gs b c d e f g h i j k l=
 m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">A014A6</span></spa=
n>)</p></th>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>=E2=AD=90</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>The following changes will be in-scope:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Beneficiary UI&nbsp;</strong>
<ol>
<li><strong>Galaxy Beneficiary MFE</strong>
<ol>
<li>Build new beneficiary management user interface that allows the CRUD of=
 beneficiaries and beneficiary accounts.</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li><strong>Beneficiary APIs</strong>
<ol>
<li><strong>Galaxy Beneficiary EXP API (Aug ERM)</strong>
<ol>
<li>Build new beneficiary management experience API that allows the CRUD of=
 beneficiaries and beneficiaries accounts.</li>
<li>Beneficiary MFE triggers payment Alias lookup endpoint and BSB lookup e=
ndpoint to validate BSB and PayID.</li>
</ol></li>
<li><strong style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Enterprise Beneficiary Managem=
ent INF API</strong><br>
<ol>
<li>Build an API layer for the beneficiary management solution, integrated =
with the Enterprise Beneficiary Management Data Store.</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li><strong>Beneficiary Datastore</strong>
<ol>
<li><strong>Enterprise Beneficiary Management Data Store</strong>&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>The database that stores the beneficiaries and beneficiary accounts dat=
a.&nbsp;</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"8207022a-81b4-47de-a50=
9-fa59c21053cf"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Ping - PLUTO Entitlem=
ents (A00CCC )</span></span></p></th>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>=E2=AD=90</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>The entitlement solution (PLUTO) will need to include beneficiary as ty=
pes of resources that can be linked to a scope.&nbsp;</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"f21368c6-b90d-4877-afe=
d-064dfea0c637"><span style=3D"text-decoration: none;">Multiverse</span> (<=
span style=3D"text-decoration: none;">A01699)</span></span></p></th>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>=E2=AD=90</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Galaxy Beneficiary MFE to be added to the OpenFin</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
