ical-align: top;" title=3D"Background colour : Light grey 100%" scope=3D"co=
l" data-highlight-colour=3D"#f4f5f7">Assumption</th>
<th class=3D"highlight-#f4f5f7 confluenceTh" style=3D"text-align: left;vert=
ical-align: top;" title=3D"Background colour : Light grey 100%" scope=3D"co=
