d>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>There is a dependency on the uplift of the payment API that returns ban=
k names based on BSB provided.</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"jira-issue resolved" data-jira-key=3D"ART-38593"> <a href=
=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au/browse/ART-38593" class=3D"jira-issue-k=
