P - Uplift BSB look up service API (Eligibility)</span> <span class=3D"aui-=
lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle             aui-lozenge-success
     jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">Done</span> </span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-01-20" class=3D"date-past">20 Jan 2025</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>D-ART-5651-002</p=
></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Dependency</p></t=
d>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>There is a dependency on the readiness of the entitlement structure cha=
nge and APIs for persisting beneficiary data to the entitlement store.</li>
<li>Potential change on the WDP client library for entitlement.</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>if Entitlement is not ready by May, e2e testing would not be possible a=
nd changes need to be done manually.</li>
<li>Entitlement initial set up will be done manually by entitlement team in=
 May.</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-01-24" class=3D"date-past">24 Jan 2025</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
