<h2 id=3D"id-01SD:BeneficiaryManagementView,create,modify,delete-KeyDecisio=
ns"><span>Ke<span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"2792b086-d66f=
-4f96-9efb-b549ecd4cf47">y Decisions</span></span></h2>
<p><span></span></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
<col>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Ref #</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Decision</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77=
);">Decision made by</span></th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Date</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">#001</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span data-teams=3D"true">decided not to progres=
s with the parent/child hierarchy and stay with the flat structure that COL=
 has.</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span data-teams=3D"true">The impacts outweigh the benefits, and we thin=
k we can give the same value through other simpler means like category labe=
ls or grouping.</span></p>
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper"><img class=3D"confluenc=
e-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" src=3D"9ecfdd801a0d38295ee167a0cc978a=
c9575872d205b8dd80a2dde4f3cc971d19" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments=
/1924182297/image-2025-2-7_9-32-14.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1=
738881134363&amp;api=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-=
resource-id=3D"1943048237" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-r=
esource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-202=
5-2-7_9-32-14.png" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" =
data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-contai=
ner-id=3D"1924182297" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"152" alt=3D=
"" width=3D"468" height=3D"193"></span></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Mel <span data-teams=3D"true">Jamieson (Product =
Owner)</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-02-06" class=3D"date-past">06 Feb 2025</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">#002</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">decision has been made not to create an extra la=
yer of institutional CAP API&nbsp;</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" heigh=
t=3D"173" src=3D"5620a4269b439093feab0b1db4004472c855e510091c32950d8bac3454=
a7ad7d" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/1924182297/image-2025-2-21_=
11-6-17.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1740096378180&amp;api=3Dv2" =
data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1954350650" =
data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment"=
 data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-2025-2-21_11-6-17.png" data-ba=
se-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-conte=
nt-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1924182297" data=
-linked-resource-container-version=3D"152" alt=3D"" width=3D"468"></span></=
p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Andrew Suduk ( Chapter lead for GTS )&nbsp;</=
p><p>Adam Oakman ( Entitlement domain architect )</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-02-21" class=3D"date-past">21 Feb 2025</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">#003</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">payloads need to be submitted along with ARCHIVE=
 endpoint&nbsp;</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>On the authorisation UI, business has confirmed they would like to see b=
elow detail for each of the below scenarios: <span class=3D"confluence-embe=
dded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence=
-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" height=3D"50" src=3D"7f374388be2eb7b84=
6efe4c0623ebb39fa7a3c6855a0ce5f3c47313bac434cb8" data-image-src=3D"/downloa=
d/attachments/1924182297/image-2025-3-10_17-16-1.png?version=3D1&amp;modifi=
cationDate=3D1741587362100&amp;api=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0=
" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1970979852" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1"=
 data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alia=
s=3D"image-2025-3-10_17-16-1.png" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.w=
estpac.com.au" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-=
resource-container-id=3D"1924182297" data-linked-resource-container-version=
=3D"152" alt=3D"" width=3D"468"></span></p>
<p>Sample authorisation UI:</p>
<p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper"><img class=3D"confluenc=
e-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" src=3D"90e41a529d923cdb679471db08a3f7=
22786433d87fd93f6cb3dfc05c9631833b" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments=
/1924182297/image-2025-3-10_17-11-25.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=
=3D1741587086157&amp;api=3Dv2" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-lin=
ked-resource-id=3D"1970979829" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-link=
ed-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image=
-2025-3-10_17-11-25.png" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.co=
m.au" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-=
container-id=3D"1924182297" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"152" =
alt=3D"" width=3D"468" height=3D"340"></span></p>
<p>In the proposed authorisation model (<a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.w=
estpac.com.au/display/ARTC/Solution+Options%3A+Checker+task+queue+handling#=
SolutionOptions:Checkertaskqueuehandling-KeyArchitectureDecisions" rel=3D"n=
ofollow">Solution Options: Checker task queue handling - Westpac One Core -=
 Westpac Enterprise Confluence</a>), payload is required as part of the req=
uest if user would like to see the detail in authorisation UI. ( which retr=
ieves detail from the Appian task queues).</p>
<p>There are two ways to achieve the business outcome:</p>
<ol>
<li>The Authorisation UI has to trigger the channel EXP API for every Archi=
ve record to retrieve the payload (which may results in performance impact =
as API call can only be made individually);&nbsp;</li>
<li>or the archive request has to include the detail as payload in the requ=
est&nbsp;</li>
</ol>
<p>As option 1 may introduce performance impact, Business has confirmed to =
proceed with the option 2 to send payload with ARCHIVE request.&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Mel <span data-teams=3D"true">Jamieson (Product =
Owner)</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2025-03-10" class=3D"date-past">10 Mar 2025</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
