ence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/ART-5651+Non-functional+requirements" =
rel=3D"nofollow">Non-Functional Requirements for ART-5651</a></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-01SD:BeneficiaryManagementView,create,modify,delete-TechnicalD=
ebt">Techn<span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"26679957-bd61-4=
ad7-81c2-26cc7bb45c32">ical De</span>bt</h2>
<p>N/A as it's a new feature.&nbsp;</p>
<h1 id=3D"id-01SD:BeneficiaryManagementView,create,modify,delete-Solution">=
<span>Solution</span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-01SD:BeneficiaryManagementView,create,modify,delete-SolutionOv=
erview"><span>Solution Overview</span></h2>
<p><span>The Solution covers at the following scenarios:</span></p>
<ol>
<li><span>Beneficiaries' creation, deletion and modification</span>
<ol>
<li><span>Enable entitled W1C users to create, modify and delete beneficiar=
ies.</span></li>
</ol></li>
<li><span>Beneficiaries viewing </span>
<ol>
<li><span>Enable entitled W1C users to view a list of beneficiaries that th=
ey are entitled to.</span></li>
</ol></li>
<li><span>Beneficiaries' storage&nbsp;</span>
<ol>
<li>New W1C owned beneficiary service and datastore for beneficiary storage=
.</li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
